		<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_08.gif"><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">DPC Vegas 4th Place</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.60)</font> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=23586">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=2392">Matt "Phobos" Berta</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=2392&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Took the good ole Uruks, put some new junk in, scrambled up the FP side real good, fried that sumtook up and served it sideways.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> May 26, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Starting~<br>
